<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870604-0172 </DOCNO><HL> Michaels May Sales Rose 25%</HL><DD> 06/04/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> MKE </IN><DATELINE> IRVING, Texas  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Michaels Stores Inc. said its May sales rose 25% to $8.1 million from $6.5 million a year earlier.    The company said sales for stores open more than one year rose 6% to $6.8 million from $6.4 million. Michaels operates specialty retail stores. </TEXT></DOC>